text_blocks.content: U.S. Department of Justice Federal Bureau of Prisons Psychological Services Metropolitan Correctional Center 150 Park Row New York, New York 10007 (646) 836-6300, (646) 836-7751 (Fax)
To: Lt. [redacted] Operations Lt. From: [redacted] Psychologist Date: 8/10/19 RE: INMATE JEFFREY EDWARD EPSTEIN #76318-054

On 8/10/19, there was a [redacted] on 9 South at about 6:35 AM. This writer responded to 9 South. Medical and other staff were already in inmate Epstein's cell giving medical attention to inmate Epstein. Staff asked for a stretcher and this writer and Officer [redacted] went to retrieve a stretcher. Officer [redacted] then asked for another AED. Officer [redacted] brought the stretcher to 9 South. This writer retrieved another AED and brought it up to 9 South. When this writer arrived at 9 South, inmate Epstein was being brought down on a stretcher to Medical.
